quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,76,"Nítorí náà, má ṣe jẹ́ kí ọ̀rọ̀ wọn bà ọ́ nínú jẹ́. Dájúdájú Àwa mọ ohun tí wọ́n ń fi pamọ́ àti ohun tí wọ́n ń ṣàfi hàn rẹ̀."
  36,77,"Ṣé ènìyàn kò wòye pé dájúdájú Àwa l’A ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ láti inú àtọ̀? (Ṣebí lẹ́yìn) ìgbà náà l’ó di alátakò pọ́nńbélé."
  36,78,"Àti pé ó fi àkàwé lélẹ̀ nípa Wa.{1} Ó sì gbàgbé ìṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀. Ó wí pé: “Ta ni Ó máa sọ egungun di alààyè nígbà tí ó ti kẹfun?”.",1:[Ìyẹn ni pé, ènìyàn ń fi agbára ẹ̀dá tí kò lè jí òkú dìde wé agbára Allāhu tí ó lè jí òkú dìde.]
  37,61,"Nítorí irú èyí, kí àwọn olùṣẹ̀sìn máa ṣẹ̀sìn lọ."
  37,62,"Ǹjẹ́ ìyẹn l’ó lóore jùlọ ní ibùdésí ni tàbí igi zaƙūm (igi ẹlẹ́gùn-ún)?"
  37,63,"Dájúdájú Àwa ṣe é ní àdánwò fún àwọn alábòsí."
  38,40,"Dájúdájú ìsúnmọ́ (Wa) àti àbọ̀ rere sì wà fún un ní ọ̀dọ̀ Wa."
  38,41,"Ṣèrántí ẹrúsìn Wa, (Ànábì)’Ayyūb. Nígbà tí ó pe Olúwa rẹ̀ (pé): “Dájúdájú aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n ti kó ìnira (àìsàn) àti ìyà bá mi.”{1}.",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah an-Nisā’ 4;79.]
  38,42,"(Mọlāika sọ fún un pé): “Fi ẹsẹ̀ rẹ janlẹ̀. Èyí ni omi ìwẹ̀ tútù àti omi mímu (fún ìwòsàn rẹ).”"
  39,25,"Àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn pe òdodo ní irọ́. Nítorí náà, ìyà dé bá wọn ní àyè tí wọn kò ti fura."
  39,26,"Allāhu fún wọn ní àbùkù ìyà tọ́ wò nínú ìṣẹ̀mí ayé yìí. Ìyà ọ̀run sì tóbi jùlọ tí ó bá jẹ́ pé wọ́n mọ̀."
  39,27,"A sì ti ṣe gbogbo àkàwé (àpèjúwe àti àpẹ̀ẹrẹ) fún àwọn ènìyàn nínú al-Ƙur’ān yìí nítorí kí wọ́n lè lo ìrántí"
  40,4,"Kò sí ẹni tí ó máa ṣe àtakò sí àwọn āyah Allāhu àfi àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́. Nítorí náà, má ṣe jẹ́ kí ìgbòkègbodò wọn nínú ìlú kó ẹ̀tàn bá ọ."
  40,5,"Ìjọ (Ànábì) Nūh pe òdodo ní irọ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Àwọn ìjọ (mìíràn) lẹ́yìn wọn (náà ṣe bẹ́ẹ̀). Ìjọ kọ̀ọ̀kan ló gbèrò láti ki Òjíṣẹ́ wọn mọ́lẹ̀. Wọ́n fi irọ́ ja òdodo níyàn nítorí kí wọ́n lè fi wó òdodo lulẹ̀. Mo sì gbá wọn mú. Nítorí náà, báwo ni ìyà (tí Mo fi jẹ wọ́n) ti rí (lára wọn ná)!"
  40,6,"Àti pé báyẹn ni ọ̀rọ̀ Olúwa rẹ ṣe kò lórí àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ pé: “Dájúdájú àwọn ni èrò inú Iná.”"